- 'Approved' means the translation has passed a review process and is considered correct;
- 'Example' refers to usage examples of the phrase.

- 'admins' refers to users with administrative privileges;
- 'viewed' refers to the action of looking at or observing an activity;
- 'phrase' refers to a specific type of activity in the system.

